Saskatchewan Extends Crop Insurance-Claim Deadline to June 30

-- B y   W h i t n e y   M c F e r r o n
-- 
2011-06-22T14:54:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/saskatchewan-extends-crop-insurance-claim-deadline-to-june-30.html
Saskatchewan extended its deadline
for farmers to submit crop-insurance claims until June 30
because of flooding and a  strike  by insurance workers.  The deadline was changed from June 20, the Canadian’s
province’s Ministry of Agriculture said today in a  statement  on
its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Whitney McFerron in Chicago at 
 wmcferron1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Stroth at 
 sstroth@bloomberg.net  